Acknowledgments
===============================================================================

This project depends on (but does not include or modify) the msi-ec kernel
module:

    Project: msi-ec - MSI Linux Embedded Controller driver
    URL:     https://github.com/BeardOverflow/msi-ec
    License: GPL-2.0

msi-ec exposes the MSI embedded controller via sysfs at
/sys/devices/platform/msi-ec/, which this userspace suite reads and writes
to. msi-power-profile is a strictly downstream consumer at the userspace
layer; no msi-ec source is vendored, redistributed, or modified by this
project, and GPL-2.0 does not propagate. Install msi-ec separately per the
upstream instructions before using this suite.
